OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,FGlasgow Central railway station will
OL,7,Fpartially reopen on Wednesday, after a
OL,8,Ffire destroyed a neighbouring building.
OL,10,FThe main part of Glasgow Central has
OL,11,Fbeen closed since Sunday, March 8,
OL,12,Fwhen the fire tore through the Union
OL,13,FCorner building, forcing Scotland's
OL,14,Fbusiest station to shut.
OL,16,FWith demolition work ongoing, much of
OL,17,FGlasgow Central will remain shut and
OL,18,Fthe area near the Gordon Street
OL,19,Fentrance will be cordoned off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
