OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,FThe Union Street and Hope Street
OL,7,Fentrances will also remain closed,
OL,8,Fwith access via the low-level
OL,9,Fentrances and the Hope Street carriage
OL,10,Fdriveway.
OL,12,FNetwork Rail said the changes mean
OL,13,Fthere will be reduced capacity and
OL,14,Fpassengers should check their journeys
OL,15,Fbefore setting off.
OL,17,FPassengers have been told the station
OL,18,Fwill "look different" and staff will
OL,19,Fbe on hand to offer advice.
OL,26,@zD@FOUzD@UO]
