OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773748974
OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,FGlasgow City Council said it is in the
OL,7,Finterests of public safety to demolish
OL,8,Fwhat remains of the "very unstable"
OL,9,FVictorian building, which was ravaged
OL,10,Fby the fire.
OL,12,FDemolition experts have been working
OL,13,Fto safely bring down parts of the
OL,14,Fremaining structure.
OL,16,FThe fire began in a vape shop on Union
OL,17,FStreet and spread through the building
OL,18,Fand around the corner, with only the
OL,19,Ffacade of the building at the junction
OL,20,Fwith Gordon Street left standing.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@cO]
