OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,FServices in the lower level of the
OL,7,Fstation began running again on
OL,8,FWednesday last week.
OL,10,FScotRail said stringent safety checks
OL,11,Fhad been carried out ahead of the
OL,12,Fpartial reopening.
OL,14,FRoss Moran, route director at Network
OL,15,FRail Scotland, said: "We're grateful
OL,16,Ffor the patience and understanding
OL,17,Fshown by passengers, businesses and
OL,18,Fthe wider community over this past
OL,19,Fweek.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
