FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773748974
OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,F"This has been an exceptionally
OL,7,Fchallenging situation for everyone
OL,8,Faffected and I want to thank all those
OL,9,Finvolved who have worked tirelessly to
OL,10,Fget us to the point where we can
OL,11,Fsafely welcome people back to the
OL,12,Fstation.
OL,14,F"While temporary arrangements will
OL,15,Fremain in place for a little while
OL,16,Flonger, we want to reassure customers
OL,17,Fthat our focus is on keeping them
OL,18,Fmoving safely as services return."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
