OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,FDavid Ross, ScotRail chief operating
OL,7,Fofficer, said: "I am very pleased we
OL,8,Fwill be able to welcome customers back
OL,9,Fto Glasgow Central high level
OL,10,Ffollowing the partial reopening of the
OL,11,Fstation from Wednesday.
OL,13,F"We realise the closure is causing
OL,14,Fsignificant disruption for our
OL,15,Fcustomers, and we're very sorry for
OL,16,Fthe impact it is still having on
OL,17,Fjourneys."
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
