OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773748974
OL,3,CGlasgow Central to partially reopen
OL,4,Cafter fire destroyed nearby building
OL,6,F"The safety of our customers and staff
OL,7,Fremains our absolute priority, and
OL,8,Fwhile we have limited platforms and
OL,9,Faccess points to the station
OL,10,Favailable, we will operate as many
OL,11,Fservices as we can," he continued.
OL,13,F"We will keep the timetable under
OL,14,Fregular review and when it is safe to
OL,15,Fadd more services we will do so."
